STATE of New Jersey, Plaintiff-Petitioner,
v.
William C. COOPER, Jr., a/k/a William Smith, and William C. Smith, Defendant-Respondent. C-725 September Term 2018
081825 Supreme Court of New Jersey. March 21, 2019

ORDER

A petition for certification of the judgment in A-001143-15 having been submitted to this Court, and the Court having considered the same;

It is ORDERED that the petition for certification is denied.
